channel.topic:
For this one we're going virtual, put Eco (Logos, A Mascot or something new) into your favorite virtual community! We're thinking Game Mods, Player Skins, Virtual Art and the like.
I know that games like VRchat and Garry's Mod let you import your own models, games like Super Mario Maker or Dreams let you make levels, Minecraft and others have plenty of ways to do Art or custom Textures.
